OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778205813
OL,3,CVotes being counted in crucial
OL,4,Celections for Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,5,Cpremiership
OL,7,FVotes are being counted in elections
OL,8,Facross Scotland, Wales and parts of
OL,9,FEngland that could prove a decisive
OL,10,Fmoment in Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,11,Fpremiership.
OL,13,FLabour is expected to suffer heavy
OL,14,Flosses throughout the country as the
OL,15,Fparty languishes in the polls and
OL,16,Ffaces challenges from Reform UK to the
OL,17,Fright and an insurgent Green Party to
OL,18,Fthe left.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778205813
OL,3,CVotes being counted in crucial
OL,4,Celections for Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,5,Cpremiership
OL,7,FPolling guru Lord Robert Hayward has
OL,8,Fsuggested Labour could lose some 1,850
OL,9,Fcouncillors in England.
OL,11,FThe party is set to lose the national
OL,12,Fvote in Wales for the first time in
OL,13,Fmore than a century, while in Scotland
OL,14,Fthe SNP appears likely to remain the
OL,15,Flargest party.
OL,17,FAs polls closed, Deputy Prime Minister
OL,18,FDavid Lammy said the elections had
OL,19,Fbeen "tough".
OL,26,@{D@FOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778205813
OL,3,CVotes being counted in crucial
OL,4,Celections for Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,5,Cpremiership
OL,7,FHe said: "I don't want to sugarcoat
OL,8,Fit, the message from the doorstep is
OL,9,Fthis is a tough election cycle.
OL,11,F"This is a mid-term set of elections
OL,12,Fwith people concerned about the cost
OL,13,Fof living and wanting to see the
OL,14,FGovernment go faster with quicker
OL,15,Fpace."
OL,17,FMr Lammy added that while Labour had
OL,18,Frun a "positive campaign", the party's
OL,19,F"message of delivery" had been
OL,20,F"drowned out by the politics of
OL,21,Fgrievance".
OL,26,@oD@JOUsD@AOUwD@FO]zD@GOUzD@YO]{D@AOU{D@
OL,26,AUO]|D@AOU}D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
