OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778205813
OL,3,CVotes being counted in crucial
OL,4,Celections for Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,5,Cpremiership
OL,7,FA national drubbing is also likely to
OL,8,Freignite speculation about Sir Keir's
OL,9,Fleadership of the party and the
OL,10,Fcountry.
OL,12,FBefore polls closed, The Times
OL,13,Freported that Energy Secretary and
OL,14,Fformer Labour leader Ed Miliband had
OL,15,Fprivately urged the Prime Minister to
OL,16,Fset out a timetable for his departure
OL,17,Fafter the elections.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778205813
OL,3,CVotes being counted in crucial
OL,4,Celections for Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,5,Cpremiership
OL,7,FOther Cabinet ministers are said to be
OL,8,Fconsidering leadership tilts,
OL,9,Fincluding Health Secretary Wes
OL,10,FStreeting and former deputy prime
OL,11,Fminister Angela Rayner.
OL,13,FAllies of Ms Rayner are confident she
OL,14,Fwould be able to gain the support of
OL,15,Fthe 81 MPs required to launch a
OL,16,Fchallenge ` a number which Mr
OL,17,FStreeting is also said to have met,
OL,18,Fthough neither is said to want to be
OL,19,Fthe first to move.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
