SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778205813
OL,3,CVotes being counted in crucial
OL,4,Celections for Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,5,Cpremiership
OL,7,FThe Greens are also expected to do
OL,8,Fwell, with new leader Zack Polanski
OL,9,Fpredicting "record-breaking local
OL,10,Felections" for the party, while Sir Ed
OL,11,FDavey's Liberal Democrats are eyeing
OL,12,Fan eighth successive year of local
OL,13,Fgains.
OL,15,FPredicting gains in London, Newcastle,
OL,16,FSussex and Wales, Mr Polanski said:
OL,17,F"The news from the doorstep is that we
OL,18,Fwill be taking seats from not just
OL,19,FLabour but the Tories and Lib Dems
OL,20,Ftoo, from all across the country."
OL,26,@qD@LOUrD@JO]yD@AOU|D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778205813
OL,3,CVotes being counted in crucial
OL,4,Celections for Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,5,Cpremiership
OL,7,FSir Ed said his party had knocked on
OL,8,Fthree million doors during the
OL,9,Fcampaign, twice its total last year,
OL,10,Fadding: "In former Conservative
OL,11,Fheartlands and old Labour strongholds
OL,12,Falike, we are standing up for decency
OL,13,Fand real change."
OL,15,FBut it could be another bad night for
OL,16,Fthe Conservatives despite an
OL,17,Fimprovement in party leader Kemi
OL,18,FBadenoch's approval rating, with the
OL,19,Fparty expected to lose further ground
OL,20,Fto Reform.
OL,26,@rD@IOUuD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
