OL,3,CVotes being counted in crucial
OL,4,Celections for Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,5,Cpremiership
OL,7,FTory chairman Kevin Hollinrake said
OL,8,Fthe party had run "an energetic and
OL,9,Fpositive campaign", but acknowledged
OL,10,Fthe elections would be "difficult"
OL,11,Fcoming two years after "a historic
OL,12,Fgeneral election defeat".
OL,14,FAlmost 25,000 candidates were fighting
OL,15,Fto be elected to more than 5,000 seats
OL,16,Fon 136 councils across England, where
OL,17,Fsix local mayoral contests also took
OL,18,Fplace.
OL,26,@pD@SOUqD@RO]rD@XOUrD@bO]sD@XOUtD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
