OL,3,CVotes being counted in crucial
OL,4,Celections for Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,5,Cpremiership
OL,7,FIn Scotland, all 129 seats were up for
OL,8,Felection at Holyrood while voters in
OL,9,FWales were choosing 96 members of the
OL,10,FSenedd.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
